            k
          
        
      
    
    {\displaystyle \sum _{k=0}^{\infty }A_{R}^{k}\beta ^{k}}
  for matrix powers or

  
    
      
        
          ∑
          
            k
            =
            0
          
          
            ∞
          
        
        
          
            
              (
              
                A
                
