            k
          
        
        (
        
          A
          
            k
          
        
        
          )
          
            j
            i
          
        
      
    
    {\displaystyle x_{i}=\sum _{k=1}^{\infty }\sum _{j=1}^{N}\alpha ^{k}(A^{k})_{ji}}
  where 
  
    
      
