    {\displaystyle r}
   and 
  
    
      
        
          σ
          
            s
            r
          
        
        (
        v
        )
      
    
    {\displaystyle \sigma _{sr}(v)}
   is the number of those paths that pass through 
  
    
      
        v
      
    
    {\displaystyle v}
  . The percolation state of the node 
  
    
      
        i
      
    
    {\displaystyle i}
   at time 
  
    
      
        t
      
    
