        i
      
    
    {\displaystyle i}
  , if 
  
    
      
        
          C
          
            x
          
        
        (
        
          p
          
            ∗
          
        
        )
      
    
    {\displaystyle C_{x}(p_{*})}
   is the largest such measure in the network, and if:

  
    
      
        max
        
          ∑
          
            i
            =
            1
          
          
            N
          
        
        (
        
          C
          
            x
          
        
